snippet.title: Wanba Warriors - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the absurd world of calligraphy combat and prepare to lay the smackdown upon all who dare to oppose you, dishing out damage with your chosen ink brush of brutality! A battle for the ages is about to commence. A battle of Wanba Warriors!

Download the demo:
itch.io: https://zdcinteractive.itch.io/wanba-warriors
Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/Wanba-Warrior/389181

Follow us on Twitter: @ZdcInteractive
